            <p class="mt-3">
              Dude, this restroom is legit! It's always clean, smells decent, and has plenty of stalls, so you don't have to wait forever. Plus, the hand dryers actually work, which is a huge bonus. Definitely my go-to spot when nature calls between classes.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-x-5 mt-5">
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-reply"></i> Reply</button>
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i> Delete</button>
