            <p class="text-grayed">posted 2 days ago</p>
            <p class="mt-3">
              Alright, this restroom is decent, I guess. It's usually clean, but sometimes you'll find a stall that needs a serious flush. The urinals are just average, nothing to write home about. It's an okay option when you're in a hurry, but don't expect anything mind-blowing.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-x-5 mt-5">
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-reply"></i> Reply</button>
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i> Delete</button>
