            <p class="mt-3">
              Okay, so this restroom is surprisingly nice. And guess what? They even have a small shelf above the sink to put your phone or keys. It's those little details that make this place stand out. Thumbs up!
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-x-5 mt-5">
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-reply"></i> Reply</button>
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i> Delete</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-x-5">
          <!-- User Icon -->
          <button type="button" class="bg-white text-black hover:opacity-80 rounded-full w-18 p-2 self-start"><i class="fa-regular fa-user"></i></button>
          <!-- Review Information -->
          <div class="flex flex-col pb-8 border-grayed border-b-2">
            <!-- Dynamically load this using JavaScript -->
            <p>
