              <i class="fa-solid fa-toilet-paper fa-rotate-270 text-grayed"></i>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-toilet-paper fa-rotate-270 text-grayed"></i>
            </p>
            <p class="text-grayed">posted 2 weeks ago</p>
            <p class="mt-3">
              Hmm, this restroom is... meh. It's usually stocked with the essentials, but don't expect any fancy extras. The air fresheners kinda help, but not enough to mask the usual bathroom odors. And the background music? Let's just say it's an acquired taste. It gets the job done, but there's nothing particularly exciting about it.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-x-5 mt-5">
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-reply"></i> Reply</button>
              <button type="button" class="hover:opacity-80"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i> Delete</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
